{"tid":1202730,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"召集海外巴絲支援義士","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:56:23.000Z","uid":87116,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3750e8c455019a214ae029d857d2974d33bad2","tid":1202730,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都聽到好多海外港人想幫手做更多，奈何只能參與各地小型集會、協助翻譯文宣等等。<br />\n<br />\n而由2014年開始，已經相繼有戰友因行動而身陷囹圄。如果大家覺得香港係需要一場真正革命的話，除咗諗戰略，亦需要有足夠後援。<br />\n<br />\n因此小弟希望可以聯合世國各地嘅港人，等之後因為政治而要逃亡嘅戰友可以有可靠渠道，到不同國家都有同道接濟。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣巴絲可以加我tg從長計議<br />\nTG: hkglobalsupport"},{"pid":"631495833e66f590cf56ea003c69556cbd154bc7","tid":1202730,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"本地巴打lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0199580bb1716b1a7b847266ffce5d0c4ad44a8","tid":1202730,"uid":210088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a29a1a11461069218fc2743ff8657efc56b0917","tid":1202730,"uid":94340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"巴打有心"},{"pid":"81843d87a086489dfe3f6006d8b8d8df0ff025dd","tid":1202730,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:56:23.000Z","msg":"幫手集中推以下呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【招募】海外港人支援！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203958/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203958/page/1</a>"}]}